-- Edison May Form Alliance for Akkas Natural-Gas Bid in Iraq, MF Reports
-- B y   A r m o r e l   K e n n a
-- 2010-09-29T05:54:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-29/edison-may-form-alliance-for-akkas-natural-gas-bid-in-iraq-mf-reports.html
Edison SpA may form an alliance
with Turkey’s Tpao to bid for a contract to develop the Akkas
natural-gas field in Iraq, newspaper MF reported, without saying
where it got the information.  China’s Cnoc may also join the group, which would be led by
Edison, according to the Italian newspaper. Bids must be
presented by Oct. 20, MF reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Armorel Kenna in Milan at 
 akenna@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jerrold Colten at 
 jcolten@bloomberg.net  